{"tid":712507,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"劉鳴煒：「讀大學不一定成功」（但識投胎就一定掂）","createTime":"2018-06-22T06:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T08:00:42.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13c453a2015c1c8662fb3f5d9a7db56904f7af2c","tid":712507,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LAv.urOTyFK5_fPJn3s6YA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/N劉ews/skypost/20180622JAB009__20180622_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLAv.urOTyFK5_fPJn3s6YA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FN%E5%8A%89ews%2Fskypost%2F20180622JAB009__20180622_L.jpg&h=0f667bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【晴報專訊】青年發展委員會副主席劉鳴煒昨出席賽馬會青年研討會，致辭時戲言要向海關舉報，指大學學位違反「商品說明條例」，大學畢業生月薪只有1.3萬元，回報率很低，甚至比職訓出來的回報還要低，呼籲學生和家長不要再單一迷戀大學就是成功的出路。他又指，現時很多履歷內容都是「遊花園」，結果聘請的人都不似預期。<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒稱，大學生畢業出來人工只是1.3萬元的因素很多，坦言明白青年或有不滿、不開心，但認為透過大學與出路有落差這說法，反映讀大學不是保證成功的因素。<br />\n<br />\n被問及他亦提到「讀書成績好可能只是考試機器」，會否抹殺好成績學生的努力和成果？劉補充說：「如果僱主需要考試好、記性好這類技能的員工，就是請對了人；相反，如果僱主需要的是溝通能力、團隊合作，我不覺得成績和分數可代表這一點。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%89%E9%B3%B4%E7%85%92-%E8%AE%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-224530018.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E7%2585%2592-%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F-224530018.html&d=sll77SUCa11LyytIORsnJkzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=894d6062\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8A%89%E9%B3%B4%E7%85%92-%E8%AE%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-224530018.html</a>"},{"pid":"ba8023a225694351dcb3bb293eee577ce1929be4","tid":712507,"uid":54337,"lik